<title>ʿạysẖ kl ḥyạty</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 ạlqrạr - ʿạysẖ kl ḥyạty mntẓr mjỷ yswʿ mn ạlsmạʾ

[V2]
 mntẓr ạkẖtṭạfy wlḥẓẗ sfry ạlạkyd mn hnạ

[V3]
 1- ʿạysẖ wlạ msẖgẖwl bạlạrḍ wmạ fyhạ

[V4]
 wkl ạlwqt bạqwl mạ lysẖ mkạn fyhạ

[V5]
 qlby wknzy fwq ʿnd yswʿ fy ạlsmạʾ

[V6]
 mntẓrẗ bkl sẖwq bạkẖdm ạlhy hnạ

[V7]
 2- mntẓr yswʿy mntẓrẗ wạnạ shrạn

[V8]
 hw sẖbʿy fy jwʿy wqlby lyẗ ʿṭsẖạn

[V9]
 kl ạsẖyạq qlby lmdynẗ ạlsmạwyẗ

[V10]
 wbạqdm kl ḥby wạnạ hnạ fy ạlbryẗ

[V11]
 3- mstʿd lmjyỷk wmqds nfsy lyk

[V12]
 wmntẓr mjyỷk frḥạn yạ ạlhy byk

[V13]
 wtkẖlṣ ạlạm ạlgẖrbẗ wạlfrḥ ạʿysẖ fyẗ

[V14]
 ạlfrḥ ạlly ṭwl ʿmry ạnạ ʿạysẖ mstnyẗ</lyrics>
